snippet: The N.F.L. fined Giants defensive end Owa Odighizuwa $12,154 for an unsportsmanlike-conduct penalty issued after he pretended to take a picture in the end zone after a touchdown....
lead_paragraph: The N.F.L. fined Giants defensive end Owa Odighizuwa $12,154 for an unsportsmanlike-conduct penalty issued after he pretended to take a picture in the end zone after a touchdown.

headline.main: Miming Photo in End Zone? Negative, the N.F.L. Says
